				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khi%E1%BA%BFu-N%C4%83ng-T%C4%A9nh/D%E1%BA%A1-t%C3%BAc-H%E1%BB%99i-An-ph%C3%B9ng-ch%E1%BB%A9c-ph%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-4X3Q60sKbi9_yaaN-B52uQ">Dạ túc Hội An phùng chức phường - 夜宿會安縫織坊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khi%E1%BA%BFu-N%C4%83ng-T%C4%A9nh/author-0k6qEpgf02Latsw5cZPrXg">Khiếu Năng Tĩnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Gi%E1%BA%A3i-mu%E1%BB%99n-k%E1%BB%B3-01/poem-pRS_AKjNTz2Ie7SpNrSq9g">Giải muộn kỳ 01 - 解悶其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-C%C6%A1/Giang-Nam-kh%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-fqNYFUlUfyFQla-5A-mq6w">Giang Nam khúc kỳ 3 - 江南曲其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-C%C6%A1/author-oVwYIEYCT983JTs6qs8v3A">Lưu Cơ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-Th%E1%BA%A1ch/H%C3%A0-B%E1%BA%AFc-d%C3%A2n/poem-dK88x5NP5ldVEcLfWVaxUA">Hà Bắc dân - 河北民</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-Th%E1%BA%A1ch/author-9cGSHCUvFAIW_3kTfbKANw">Vương An Thạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/H%E1%BA%A1-d%E1%BA%A1-v%E1%BA%A5n-b%E1%BB%91c-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-H%C3%A0nh-Ph%E1%BB%A7/poem-WlFe629xtdJnuLqmN_N1tg">Hạ dạ vấn bốc đồng Hành Phủ - 夏夜問卜同衡甫</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/H%C3%A0n-th%E1%BB%B1c-d%C3%A3-v%E1%BB%8Dng-ng%C3%A2m/poem-DIUVHKV7QRA4lIdF-IbzIA">Hàn thực dã vọng ngâm - 寒食野望吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Ch%E1%BA%A9n/Khi%E1%BB%83n-bi-ho%C3%A0i-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-FnBubxd2yYKq-2rgrFn6UQ">Khiển bi hoài kỳ 2 - 遣悲懷其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Ch%E1%BA%A9n/author-bMSP5YOXWyK1jTzTI9MKNQ">Nguyên Chẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/T%E1%BA%BF-tr%E1%BA%ADn-vong/poem-JnHWJb5Kd6-M07NFz1l5Zw">Tế trận vong - 祭陣亡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/author-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Ti%C3%AAu-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Khanh-th%C3%AA-%C4%90%E1%BB%87-tam-%C4%91o%E1%BA%A1n/poem-trmlveecyzF5LgQn_FnFAQ">Tiêu Trọng Khanh thê - Đệ tam đoạn - 焦仲卿妻－第三段</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C4%83n-H%E1%BB%99c-T%C6%B0-l%E1%BB%A5c-quan-v%E1%BB%8B-quy/poem-LB7dbbdCGM-hnrqEfAiwyw">Văn Hộc Tư lục quan vị quy - 聞斛斯六官未歸</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
